ExternalData.Subtitlesect: Extension with modifications of the International Coffee Agreement, 1968, approved by the International Coffee Council in resolution No. 264 of 14 April 1973*
ExternalData.EIF: 1 October 1973. The Agreement was extended by the Protocol for the continuation in force of the International Coffee Agreement, 1968, as extended on 1 October 1975 [see chapter XIX.5 c)].
